    <title>html (三)  列表&表格</title>
    <url>/2019/11/19/html%20(%E4%B8%89)%20%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8&amp;%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h4><ul>
<li><p><strong>ol&amp;li</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li><p>ordered  list &amp; list item</p>
</li>
<li><p>有序列表，&lt; ol &gt;中只能嵌套&lt; li &gt;,&lt; li &gt;中可以嵌套其他元素</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p><strong>ul&amp;li</strong>  </p>
<ul>
<li><p>unordered list &amp; list item</p>
</li>
<li><p>无序列表，&lt; ul &gt;中只能嵌套&lt; li &gt;,&lt; li &gt;中可以嵌套其他元素</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p><strong>dl&amp;dt&amp;dd</strong>  </p>
<ul>
<li><p>desciption list &amp;   description term  &amp;   description description </p>
</li>
<li><p>自定义列表</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span>计算机<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>用来计算的仪器 ... ...<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span>显示器<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>以视觉方式显示信息的装置 ... ...<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h4><p><strong>table</strong> 标签定义 HTML 表格。简单的 HTML 表格由 table 元素以及一个或多个 <strong>tr</strong>、<strong>th</strong> 或 <strong>td</strong> 元素组成；由<strong>thead</strong>（一个tabel只能有一个thead），<strong>tbody，tfoot</strong>组成表单结构。</p>
<p><strong>标签</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><p>table ： 表格</p>
</li>
<li><p>tr 行</p>
</li>
<li><p>th 表头</p>
</li>
<li><p>td 表数据</p>
</li>
<li><p>colgroup</p>
<ul>
<li>用于对<strong>col标签</strong>进行组合，以便对其进行格式化。添加class属性就能用css来设置样式。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>属性</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><p>colspan ： 设置跨列</p>
</li>
<li><p>rowspan： 设置跨行</p>
<ul>
<li>设置了跨行或跨列，相应需要删除多余的表格（td）</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>border-spacing：边框间距</p>
</li>
<li><p>cellspacing：边框间距</p>
<p><strong>实例1</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="/2019/11/19/html%20(%E4%B8%89)%20%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8&%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC/table.png" alt="table"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span>表格标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>姓名<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>性别<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>年龄<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>籍贯<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>寝室<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 第一行元素设置了跨行和跨列 ，相应需要减少第一行的td(5=2+2+1)，减少第二行的td（5=1+1+2+1）--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">colspan</span>=<span class="string">"2"</span> &gt;</span>tom<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">colspan</span>=<span class="string">"2"</span> <span class="attr">rowspan</span>=<span class="string">"2"</span>&gt;</span>男<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>201<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>实例2</strong></p>
<p><img src="/2019/11/19/html%20(%E4%B8%89)%20%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8&%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC/colgroup.png" alt="colgroup"></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">"1"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 用于对列进行分组，以列为单位设置样式 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">colgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">col</span> <span class="attr">span</span>=<span class="string">"2"</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">"background-color:red"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">col</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">"background-color:yellow"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">colgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>ISBN<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>Title<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>Price<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>3476896<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>My first HTML<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>$53<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>5869207<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>My first CSS<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>$49<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="map-amp-area"><a href="#map-amp-area" class="headerlink" title="map &amp; area"></a>map &amp; area</h4><ul>
<li><p>map :  映射标签</p>
<ul>
<li>usemap的属性值和map元素的“id”或者“name”相等</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>area ： 圈定map中位置</p>
<blockquote>
<p>​    shape=”rect”  矩形对角点坐标 “ x1，y1，x2，y2 ”</p>
<p>​    shape=”circle” 圆坐标 圆心+半径  “  x1，y1，r “</p>
<p>​    shape=”poly” 路径坐标 “ x1，y1，x2，y2，x3，y3，xn，yn ”    </p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/tiy/t.asp?f=html_areamap" target="_blank" rel="noopener">实例</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p><strong>参考</strong>：</p>
<p> <a href="https://www.zhangxinxu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.zhangxinxu.com/</a> </p>
<p> <a href="https://babopo.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://babopo.github.io/</a> </p>
<p> <a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.w3school.com.cn/</a> </p>
<p> <a href="https://www.runoob.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.runoob.com/</a> </p>
]]></content>
